      </div>
      <h2 className="text-white text-2xl font-black mb-4 tracking-tight">OS Bridge Required</h2>
      <p className="text-zinc-400 text-sm mb-8 leading-relaxed max-w-xs">Redo Pro must establish a secure link with your phone's Camera and GPS hardware.</p>

      <div className="w-full space-y-3 mb-10">
